description:
On Today's Episode of the Dan Patrick Show, DP recaps last night's game between the Mavs and Clippers. Luka only scored 22 points, which means the boys will have to pay off a bet. NBA HOF/NBA on TNT analyst Charles Barkley, Colts new QB Philip Rivers and TNT/Yahoo's Chris Haynes all join the program.
